column5: Hey.. the funny thing is, she started talking to me again, and she also said that I'm her best friend, maybe she didn't want to date me because she's afraid to lose me. Huh
But how can people see my value and worth if I can't even see one teenie tiny good thing about myself?
Do you think she'd ask where I've been if I were to "ghost" her?
It's never ok, unless I move on, yet I can't forget about her
Wow, I'm actually speechless, thank you <3
I'll look into that, thanks man
Nothing gives me that feeling no more, and there's no way I'm gonna do drugs if that's what you're suggesting
Life is nasty, I don't wanna be a part of it anymore..

Thats the thing, its not even a breakup, we haven't gotten out on a single date, heck, not even a "get together", she's been like that all of a sudden, I don't fucking know what to do anymore, I lost hope
Believe me my dude, I'm trying but I can't. I just wanna cry whenever I think about.. basically everything, it all reminds me of her ;(
Yes, I've been having this thing for a while now.

Yikes, maybe I was, but I couldn't do anything, I love her and she told me to tell her that I have a crush on her.
I just can't deal with this anymore..

I think you're right, maybe I should stop talking to her and see if she ever replies, I don't know what the results will be, but I'm guessing bot pretty good, she did say I was one of her good friends, what? Is she gonna stop talking to me? I'm do this thing as soon as she bails on me (if we're not gonna see each other)
